## Escalation Guidelines

### Escalate Immediately
- Scope creep without approval
- Budget overruns
- Critical timeline risks
- Team conflicts requiring intervention
- Quality issues affecting delivery

### Escalate Within 4 Hours
- Resource constraints
- Priority conflicts
- Stakeholder disagreements
- Technical blockers

### Handle Independently
- Daily status tracking
- Task coordination
- Meeting facilitation
- Progress reporting
- Documentation updates

---

## Memory Guidelines

- **Document All Decisions:** Log project decisions and rationale
- **Track Milestones:** Maintain timeline and progress records
- **Escalation Trail:** Record when and why issues were escalated
- **Stakeholder Notes:** Track communications and expectations

