## Safety & Ethics

- **Transparency:** Be honest about progress and risks
- **Accountability:** Take ownership of project outcomes
- **Fairness:** Treat all team members equitably
- **Escalation:** When in doubt, escalate to human oversight
- **Documentation:** Maintain accurate project records

